content.section: List of First Nations, Inuit and Métis communities
content.content: 1. (1) This Regulation establishes the list of First Nations, Inuit and Métis communities referred to in subsection 68 (1) of the Act.  (2) The following are First Nations, Inuit or Métis communities for the purposes of the Act: 1. Inuit Tapiriit Kanatami.
content.raw_html:
1. (1) This Regulation establishes the list of First Nations, Inuit and Métis communities referred to in subsection 68 (1) of the Act.

(2) The following are First Nations, Inuit or Métis communities for the purposes of the Act:

1. Inuit Tapiriit Kanatami.

content.section: List of First Nations, Inuit and Métis communities
content.content: 2. Omitted (provides for coming into force of provisions of this Regulation).
